  <ThingDef ParentName="ApparelArmorPowerSolarBase">
    <defName>BOR_Solar_Apparel_PowerArmor</defName>
    <label>solar marine armor</label>
    <description>A suit of solar powered armor. Layered sunsteel-weave plates are very effective at stopping attacks, with few vulnerable joint sections. Neuro-memetic assistors allow a human to wear the armor and still move easily.\n\nArmor like this is often used by rapid-incursion space marines.</description>
    <apparel>
      <tags>
        <li>SpacerMilitary</li>
      </tags>
    </apparel>
    <recipeMaker>
      <displayPriority>105</displayPriority>
    </recipeMaker>
  </ThingDef>

